### -------------------- Classes --------------------

### 1) Add class (supervisor is teacher id, children is array of child ids)
POST {{baseUrl}}/class
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "_id": 100,
  "name": "A1",
  "supervisor": 1,
  "children": [10]
}

### 2) Get all classes
GET {{baseUrl}}/class

### 3) Get class by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/class/100

### 4) Update class by id
PUT {{baseUrl}}/class/100
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "A1 Updated",
  "children": [10]
}

### 5) Delete class by id
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/class/100

### 6) Get class children (returns full child docs)
GET {{baseUrl}}/classchildern/100

### 7) Get class supervisor teacher (returns full teacher doc)
GET {{baseUrl}}/classTeacher/100
